{
  "_comment": "Account pool configuration for Gantry. Enables centralized credential management instead of per-agent credentials.",
  "_docs": "https://github.com/geleynse/gantry/blob/main/docs/account-pool.md",
  "_usage": "Set 'accountPool' in gantry.json to the path of this file. Gantry will auto-assign available accounts to agents at startup.",

